summary: I’m not on social media because I don’t think I’m very thick skinned. People forget: they can put something into their phone...
text: I’m not on social media because I don’t think I’m very thick skinned. People forget: they can put something into their phone about someone they’ve never met and it sends and they have no repercussions, no reason to think that they’ve hurt anyone. On occasion, I’ve read something I shouldn’t have done and I’ll stay awake, cry and go into a depression. In the grand scheme of things, it probably [wasn’t even] that mean, but I am not able to cope with it.

Welcome to my tumblr.

My name is Amanda. I am graphic designer and free lance artist. I live in Tallahassee, Fl with my husband Mike and our pack of chihuahuas. I love mid century modern design, sci-fi, animation, stand up comedy, Doctor Who, home projects, subverting the dominant paradigm, anime and philosophy. I'm what you might call a renaissance woman.

Prepare for randomness and geekery.

summary: So 💯 % of you said to finish this one. Thanks y’all. I have a tradition of drawing Rose and Tentoo every Christmas. The...
body: So 💯 % of you said to finish this one. Thanks y’all. I have a tradition of drawing Rose and Tentoo every Christmas. The galavanting across Europe kinda got in the way but I did start this then. It was @colabug417 idea to make it NYE instead. Now when I look at this I’m reminded of the epic fireworks show husbot & I saw on the bay in Amsterdam on the Queen Elizabeth II.
